t: ASATEX AG - Company Profile and Products | Metoree
s: Asatex AG, founded in 1982 and headquartered in Bergheim, North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany, is a personal protective clothing and equipment designer, manufacturer, and supplier. The company's products include disposable protective clothing, antistatic clothing, and hazardous chemical PPE. It also offers PPE for flame and welding protection, as well as high-visibility workwear. The company owns numerous brands ...
